{
  "stem": "22652.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she would sometimes say, if I didn't have to hide you, I could have a nice hunk of ham or salami.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if the check from the social welfare agency came late, she would beat me severely.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so I was cold and hungry, and I was beaten up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one time, we had coupons to get bread at the local bakery in the village, and I lost the money and the coupon that she gave me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I came in and told her, and she beat me till I almost passed unconscious.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she said, don't come back till you get the bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You find a way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So when I went back to the bakery, and he saw I was all beaten up and in tears, he gave me loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I also want to mention, it's kind of funny, but we all have ways of earning a living.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She had the field.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so it was a big deal to pick up the dung from the horse, or, or mules, or donkeys that went down the road.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I used to go after school, and I'd run after the horses, donkeys, and mules.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'd pick-- with my bare hand-- I'd pick up the dung, and put it in the bag.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I had a decent meal that day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was very happy when I did that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I learned to make a living early in life to pay for my room and board.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The rural school teacher was a husband and wife team, and a gentleman from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would-- I never mentioned that I was Jewish, but they, they knew things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so one day, a social worker came and took me out of there.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
